A mother's dementia reignites a past of crime and lust, forcing her daughter to make difficult decisions.
After a boy loses his sister's pair of shoes, he goes on a series of adventures in order to find them. When he can't, he tries a new way to "win" a new pair.

After a drunken house party with his straight mates, Russell heads out to a gay club. Just before closing time he picks up Glen but what's expected to be just a one-night stand becomes something else, something special.
On the night of the discovery of a duplicate Earth in the Solar system, an ambitious young student and an accomplished composer cross paths in a tragic accident.
After saving a Black Panther from some racist cops, a black male prostitute goes on the run from "the man" with the help of the ghetto community and some disillusioned Hells Angels.
Coming-of-age story about a suave 15-year-old prep school student who falls in love with his stepmother. When her best friend responds to his advances, he suddenly finds himself in way over his head.
A modern-day musical about a busker and an immigrant and their eventful week in Dublin, as they write, rehearse and record songs that tell their love story.
A writer documents the journey his family takes to Mongolia to consult with nomadic shamans on the healing of their autistic son.
A self-focused BMX dirt rider aspires to become the next stunt champion and is forced to mentor a troubled teen.
Depressed at the commercialism he sees around him, Charlie Brown tries to find a deeper meaning to Christmas.
A documentary that captures the making of a fine art photographic book featuring 16 of the world's most successful adult film stars.
Three teenagers' quest to qualify for the 2012 US Olympic table tennis team.
Director Michael Moore pursues GM CEO Roger B. Smith to confront him about the harm he did to Flint, Michigan with his massive downsizing.

A talented young filmmaker from New York sets off to Los Angeles in pursuit of the Hollywood dream, only to discover through his relationship with a beautiful feisty young actress, that Hollywood is not all that it seems.
Two documentary filmmakers attempt to penetrate a cult who worships a woman who claims to be from the future.

Iris invites her friend Jack to stay at her family's island getaway after the death of his brother. At their remote cabin, Jack's drunken encounter with Hannah, Iris' sister, kicks off a revealing stretch of days.
Nat Turner, a literate slave and preacher in the antebellum South, orchestrates an uprising.
A losing coach with an underdog football team faces their giants of fear and failure on and off the field to surprising results.

20 years after a horrific accident during a small town school play, students at the school resurrect the failed show in a misguided attempt to honor the anniversary of the tragedy - but soon discover that some things are better left alone.

An actor limited to stereotypical roles because of his ethnicity, dreams of making it big as a highly respected performer. As he makes his rounds, the film takes a satiric look at African American actors in Hollywood.
Two young boys, both social outcasts in their small town, form an unlikely friendship.
A bad scientist and wife, a mad scientist and skeleton, two aliens and their escaped pet are all searching for the elusive element "atmospherium".
Left home alone with his dog Harry, young Ray finds himself in a bit of trouble when Harry gets loose in the suspicious neighbor's house and accidentally knocks over a top-secret invisibility potion.
A scheming couple put a struggling family man and his old friend through a series of increasingly twisted dares over the course of an evening at a local bar.
A documentary that follows the journeys of indie game developers as they create games and release those works, and themselves, to the world.
After surviving a gang rape and mugging, a middle aged businesswoman and her 23 year old boyfriend plot to murder their attackers, but find themselves conflicted about carrying out their plans.
In a Scandinavian insane asylum, murderer Salem sneaks-out at night to exact his revenge on those who he deems responsible for his predicament.
A paranoid mathematician searches for a key number that will unlock the universal patterns found in nature.
A young girl steals her dad's growth experiment infused grapes and feeds them to a pet crab. Years later, the now gigantic crustacean attacks the town!
While examining the influence of the fast food industry, Morgan Spurlock personally explores the consequences on his health of a diet of solely McDonald's food for one month.
In a post apocalyptic future, two rival gangs fight for control of Frazier Park by playing "Beat Beat Revelation", a deadly version of Dance, Dance, Revolution(TM).

After a break up, Jenny moves in with writer Kelly, her filmmaker husband, and their child. Despite a rocky start, Jenny's influence helps Kelly realize that an evolution in her life, career and relationship is necessary for her happiness.
In the small Central California town where they grew up, two estranged gay brothers struggle to reconnect after the recent death of their father.
Two New York film editors balance their personal relationships while reworking a movie in crisis.
A woman and her sister begin to link a mysterious tunnel to a series of disappearances, including that of her own husband.
Three Irish Catholic brothers from Long Island struggle to deal with love, marriage, and infidelity.
Two best friends are filming a comedy about getting revenge on the bullies at their high school. One of them isn't joking.
About a recent college grad who returns home while she tries to figure out what to do with her life.
A college student returning home for Halloween is forced to face his childhood fears when an escaped killer takes refuge in his family's "Haunted Hayride".
While sorting the affairs of his late Uncle, a man accidentally stumbles across a series of dark secrets connected to an ancient horror waiting to be freed.
An intimate documentary exploring the lost art of the oldetime strongman and one man's struggle to overcome limitations of body and mind.
On a road trip, Nic and two friends are drawn to an isolated area by a computer genius. When everything suddenly goes dark, Nic regains consciousness - only to find himself in a waking nightmare.
Martin Bonner has just moved to Nevada from the East Coast, leaving behind his two adult children and a life he spent more than two decades building.
A True Story. Based on Things That Never Actually Happened. ...And Some That Did.
Mike and Matt own nothing and share everything, including their life's work, a screenplay, which seems to be their only escape from the harsh reality that is the Hollywood machine.
A group of college students travel to a small Texas town to research the Legend of Blood Lake, an obscure folktale forged by events surrounding the horrible massacre of a Comanche village.
A film account and presentation of the final concert of The Band.
Five girls, one secret. Revenge stalks them in the night.
On a summer break from college, a young epileptic woman struggles to balance her feelings for her fledgling boyfriend while her friend Al crashes with her for the season.

Alan is a musician who leaves a busted-up band for New York, and a new musical voyage. He tries to stay focused and fends off all manner of distractions, including the attraction to his good friend's girlfriend.
Crew of "Paranormal Legends" went to film their 4th season at the place where La Llorona (Weeping woman) was reportedly seen. Only thing that's left was 17 hours of tapes and 2 camcorders.
A crime family looks to unmask the police informant in their midst who threatens to take down their business.
A day in the lives of two convenience clerks named Dante and Randal as they annoy customers, discuss movies, and play hockey on the store roof.

Two business executives--one an avowed misogynist, the other recently emotionally wounded by his love interest--set out to exact revenge on the female gender by seeking out the most innocent, uncorrupted girl they can find and ruining her life.
A man with a thirst for revenge builds a full body armor from Kevlar and goes on a killing spree.
A day in the life of Austin, Texas as the camera roams from place to place and provides a brief look at the overeducated, the social misfits, the outcasts and the oddballs.
A desperate ex-con is forced to gather his old crew for one last job to pay off his sister's debt to a dangerous local criminal.
A group of teenagers accidentally release an evil spirit that starts to possess them one by one.
A young New York couple intricately strategize their own break up.
After she ends up in prison and loses custody of her son, a woman struggles to assimilate outside her former life and remain clean long enough to regain custody of her son.

Recently dumped by his girlfriend for another man, working in a job he hates, things could be better for Peter. One night, while he is alone in his apartment, there is a knock at the door. His life will never be the same again.
A frustrated detective deals with the case of several gruesome murders committed by people who have no recollection of what they've done.
Sex, drums, tequila, social networking, a pirate, morning after pills, Jesus and a gun. It's one hot mess!
Four friends/fledgling entrepreneurs, knowing that there's something bigger and more innovative than the different error-checking devices they've built, wrestle over their new invention.
A traveling mariachi is mistaken for a murderous criminal and must hide from a gang bent on killing him.
Newlyweds Buzzy and Katie find their blissful life disrupted by the arrival of his half-sister and news of her sister's marriage troubles.
A two-hour backdoor pilot of the TV series with the same name that focuses on four postal workers who take it upon themselves to track down intended recipients of undeliverable mail.
A brilliant and charismatic, yet psychotic serial killer communicates with other active serial killers and activates a cult of believers following his every command.
A surreal take on the zombie genre.

A New York attorney is sent to Shanghai on business, where he finds himself in a legal mess that threatens his career. With the help of a relocation specialist and her contacts, he soon learns to appreciate the wonders of Shanghai.
